<h3><b>The University Library</b></h3>
<hr> <hr>
The library was founded in 2003 with a few book racks and some donated books. Now it is a 
fully functional hybrid library where it is now possible to access information about the 
physical items as well as the digital holdings in the form of e-books and e-journals, multimedia 
CDROMs and software from any where through a single unified web based interface i.e  from 
the official portal that is ( library portal http://university.libcarecloud.com ) .
<br> <br>
The Library has both e - resources and print resources. It has a total collection of approx 23000 
print books with 8000 ( Aprox.) title. The university also have 10131 e-books. The university 
also have e-journals from IEEE , Indian Journals.com etc. 
The university is getting 5,616,071 ( approx.) items from IEL online among which we have 
1,199,171 e-journals, 4,185,735 conference proceedings, 201,390 magazines, 5055 standards.
The library also has a good collection of CDs, audio Cassette and DVD . 
<hr> <hr>

